text: The Team 'Aero Kickboxing without Step' category involved eight teams representing seven countries from two continents (Europe and North America). Each team went through five performances (1.5 to 2 minutes each) with the totals added up at the end of the event. The gold medal winner was Team Hungary who won their second gold in the Aero Kickboxing team events, Team Slovenia claimed silver and Team Croatia II claimed bronze. ==Results== {| class="wikitable" |- !
